## 🎯 **COMPLEXITY-BASED AUTOMATIC ROUTING**

### **Smart Mode Selection**

The system automatically routes tasks to the appropriate mode(s) based on complexity:

- **Level 1**: ⚒️ **Operational Only** (Quick fixes, simple tasks)
- **Level 2**: 🎨 **Tactical → ⚒️ Operational** (Enhancements, features)
- **Level 3**: 🎭 **Strategic → 🎨 Tactical → ⚒️ Operational** (Complex features, systems)
- **Level 4**: 🎭 **Strategic → 🎨 Tactical → ⚒️ Operational → 🎭 Reflection** (Architecture, enterprise)

### **Automatic Complexity Detection**

```mermaid
graph TD
    Start["Task Description"] --> Keywords{"Keyword Analysis"}
    
    Keywords -->|"Fix/Bug/Error"| L1["Level 1<br>⚒️ Operational Only"]
    Keywords -->|"Add/Update/Improve"| L2["Level 2<br>🎨 Tactical → ⚒️ Operational"]
    Keywords -->|"Implement/Create/Build"| L3["Level 3<br>🎭 Strategic → 🎨 Tactical → ⚒️ Operational"]
    Keywords -->|"System/Architecture"| L4["Level 4<br>Full Cycle with Reflection"]
    
    L1 --> Route1["Direct Implementation"]
    L2 --> Route2["Quick Planning → Execution"]
    L3 --> Route3["Full Planning Cycle"]
